      <title>好时公司寻求 CFTC 批准在纽约购买大量可可库存</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/hershey-seeks-cftc-help-to-take-huge-cocoa-position-in-new-york</link>
